snippet.title: Instruments of Destruction - v1.1 and Console Trailer
snippet.description:
Instruments of Destruction is a vehicle-action game with advanced physics-based destruction, coming to Playstation 5 and Xbox Series X/S on March 27th, 2025.  Instruments of Destruction version 1.1 is now available on Steam:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1428100/Instruments_of_Destruction/
